name: math_test_3
title: Math GED Practice Test 4 v2015.06 (c)
intro_text:
Mathematics

Welcome to the Mathematics Practice Test.

You have 58 minutes to complete the test. There are 25 questions. The goal is to give you practice on the types of questions you will see on the GED® test and to give you a study plan for what you need to brush up on for the test.

If you are unsure of an answer click "Review Question Later" to come back to the question later. There are three versions of the Mathematics Practice Test. You will be able to retake the tests as often as you choose.

The first set of questions will evaluate your calculation skills, and will not have a calculator available.
